<p>Cargue archivos PDF y documentos que me ayuden a comprender el tema y a realizar mejores modificaciones.</p></li></ul></section></div><div class="mt-[var(--composer-container-height)]" style="height: 0px; overflow: hidden;"></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-12 flex justify-center bg-background-100 px-6 text-center dark:bg-background-150" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="space-y-8 pb-8 text-foreground-450 text-sm dark:text-foreground-600" style="opacity: 1;">Copilot es una inteligencia artificial y puede cometer errores. Tus conversaciones son personalizadas y ayudan a entrenar la inteligencia artificial. <button class="text-foreground-450 text-sm dark:text-foreground-600 underline" type="button" title="">Optar por no recibir</button>.</div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 w-full"><div class="absolute inset-x-3 inset-y-0"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute size-full bg-background-100 dark:bg-background-150 before:from-background-100 dark:before:from-background-150 before:absolute before:-top-8 before:h-8 before:w-full before:bg-gradient-to-t before:to-transparent"></div></div><div class="flex w-full flex-col"><div class="relative bottom-0 flex min-h-composer w-full items-end gap-1.5 pb-3 pe-3 ps-2"><input accept="image/jpeg,.jpg,.jpeg,image/png,.png,image/webp,.webp,image/svg+xml,.svg,text/plain,.txt,application/pdf,.pdf,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document,.docx,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet,.xlsx,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.presentationml.presentation,.pptx,application/json,.json,application/xml,.xml,text/csv,.csv,text/markdown,.md,text/javascript,.js,text/css,.css,text/html,.html,.htm,text/xml,.xml" class="hidden" type="file"><div class="relative bottom-0"><button type="button" class="relative flex items-center text-foreground-800 fill-foreground-800 active:text-foreground-600 active:fill-foreground-600 dark:active:text-foreground-650 dark:active:f